long_description: Protect your bike and other equipment against thieves with the Kabeltek high-carbon steel Flexweave cable. Woven cable is made from high-carbon steel with brass; stronger then most other cables on the market that use gray, aircraft-grade steel. Aluminum swaged ends are strong and durable. Vinyl-coated to protect your bikes finish- also contains U.V. inhibitors for long-lasting durability. Not to be used for towing. Must purchase lock separately.
